  "privacyIntro": "At {appName}, your Yksityisyys is paramount. This Yksityisyys Policy explains how we collect, use, store, and protect your personal and health-related data. By using our services, you agree to the practices described below.",
  "privacySectionDataCollection": "1. Tietojen kerääminen",
